大威脅[/red]，嚴重破壞社會秩序，社會應予以最強烈譴責。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n除咗班衝出嚟柒既福建幫之外有咩市民既安全係受示威者威脅<br />\n我淨係見到深水埗居民個肺好危險<br />\n元朗市民人身好撚唔安全<br />\n同埋全港市民安全受狗隻威脅"},{"pid":"e4d551b6b26fdee5ec1bcda2d813c6ef0429f609","tid":1610853,"uid":256143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"生命受威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請問最後警隊有邊個受重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2442d86f5a8364ba316b6eb191b762b6b879922","tid":1610853,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:14:59.000Z","msg":"閱。哦。"},{"pid":"26e533c6381a541e0e2bacb3f57ea6d36d99aa14","tid":1610853,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:15:49.000Z","msg":"邊個星期唔譴責同憤慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739aaf8a05e20b1033f655d7da71a2b5743ff973","tid":1610853,"uid":265881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:24:05.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"244262fe9f51eb713407b7ffd5480b5cddf1c24f","tid":1610853,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:31:22.000Z","msg":"呢個非法政府講嘢仲有人理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70f87464cda85af25ba64470064fd84e22f6b83","tid":1610853,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:38:12.000Z","msg":"掉水樽同掉汽油彈都係告暴動同最嚴厲譴責既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f20679b743ecc4b61ee235ee466088c74372e6","tid":1610853,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d551b6b26fdee5ec1bcda2d813c6ef0429f609","tid":1610853,"uid":256143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"生命受威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl